<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me - Application for Unity</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #ff6f61;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #ff6f61;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        nav a {
            color: white;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            color: #ffd1c4;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .about-section {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .about-section h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .about-section p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Me - Application for Unity</h1>
    </header>
    <%- include('./partials/nav') %>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>Hello! My name is Omri Kaslasi, and I'm excited to apply for a position at Unity. With a passion for DevOps, software development, and learning, I believe I can contribute significantly to Unity's mission of empowering creators worldwide.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Professional Experience</h2>
            <p>I have over 10 years of experience in the tech industry, specializing in DevOps. In my previous roles, I have successfully managed large-scale infrastructure projects, and collaborated with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality software solutions.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Skills and Expertise</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>DevOps: CI/CD, automation, infrastructure as code, cloud services (AWS, Azure)</li>
                <li>Tools: Kubernetes, Docker, Git, Terraform</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>2024 Kaslasi Omri | Application for Unity</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
